description: Central on  Broadway is the newest luxury building in South Boston!  This prime location is home to 18 residential units that wrap an open rotunda. Unit 104 is a Two Bedroom, 2 1/2 Bath with amazing open space with tons of windows. The kitchen features a large center island with seating area, stainless appliances, quartz counters and custom cabinetry.  There is ample room for entertaining is the open concept that looks out over the intersecting Broadway Streets and Dorchester Ave. A half bathroom at the entry services guests and the bedroom has an adjacent full bathroom with an amazing rain shower and designer tile. Ross surround sound system. Garage parking for one car. More units are to come as we launch this premiere building.
